        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "The empty definition term which is placed using Zend_Form when no label is specified (for example a submit button) is not XHTML valid. Therefore I suggest that, if the doctype is set to XHTML, the wrapper either doesn't place the empty definition term <dt><\/dt>, or places a nonbraking space inside it <dt>&nbsp;<\/dt>."
